Package: libqtzdata0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libqt5core5a (>= 5.9) , libqt5sql5 (>= 5.9) , libqtzcore0 (>= 0.4)
Description: Qtz is a Qt-based Application Development Framework.
 QtzData supports:
    * Asynchronous Data Model (Thanks to obeezzy)
    * Database Integration Backend (multiple vendors)
    * Data Management Utilities (vendor-agnostic backup, restore, encryption tools)
    * Data Analysis Tools

Package: libqtzdata-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libqtzdata0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends} , qtbase5-dev (>= 5.9) , libqtzcore-dev (>= 0.4)
Description: This package provides development files to use libqtzdata
 You need to install this package, only if you want to develop software using 
 libqtzdata
